This chrome extension use for click to dial any number from chrome browser developed by Elisha Telecom (www.elishatelecom.com).

Click To Dial Chrome Extension provides click to dial facility from Vincere CRM web portal by selecting telephone number from their contact list. 

This Click To Dial Chrome Extension from Elisha Telecom helps to call from Vincere CRM systems.

Features of Click To Dial Chrome Extension

 # Click to dial From Chrome web browser to any number.
 # Easy to use.
 # Provides a quick call facility.
 # Save time of typing a phone number.
 # Simple configuration.
 # Increase dialling speed.
 # Integration of Click To Dial Chrome Extension
